Final Interview Wrap-Up (Important)

A good closing statement:

To summarize, I designed a scalable Jira-like system with microservices for issue management, workflows, and notifications. The system uses PostgreSQL for structured data, Redis for caching, Elasticsearch for search, Kafka for asynchronous events, and object storage for attachments. This architecture ensures scalability, reliability, and efficient collaboration for large teams.\

