How Atlassian Actually Scales Jira

  Atlassian uses several techniques.
  Microservices
  
  Jira Cloud is broken into services:
  Issue Service
  Identity Service
  Search Service
  Notification Service

Search
  Uses Elasticsearch clusters.

Storage
  Uses:
  PostgreSQL
  distributed storage for attachments

Event Streaming
  Uses Kafka for event pipelines.

Multi-Tenancy
  Jira Cloud hosts multiple organizations with tenant isolation.

